#################################################################################
#  README
#
#  This suite of scripts provides a simple interface to update packages on
#    Arch Linux.
#
#  DEPENDENCIES:  pacman
#		  pacmatic (optiopnal)
#
#  Files:
#	CONFIG_SETUP
#	CONFIG_FUNCS_TEMPLATE
#
#
#	CONFIG_FUNCS_CREATOR:	Uses CONFIG_FUNCS_BUILDER to create CONFIG_FUNCS
#	CONFIG_SETUP:			Master script uses CONFIG_FUNCS to install all needed
#						files, folders, packages for a fully operational new install.
#
#  USE: Make sure that all scripts are executable, and folder is on your $PATH:
#	     $ cd ~/bin/PACMAN			       # cd into script folder
#	     $ chmod +x update.pacman.sh reflector.sh
#	     $ echo $PATH
#
#
#  $ update.pacman.sh
#
#  NB:
#################################################################################
